        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-gold"></span>
          <span class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gold font-medium">Projenizi Konuşalım</span>
          <span class="w-8 h-px bg-gold"></span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Hayalinizdeki Mekanı Tasarlayalım</h2>
        <p class="text-white/40 mb-8 max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed">Ücretsiz keşif ve fiyat teklifi için WhatsApp'tan yazın ya da arayın. En kısa sürede size dönüyoruz.</p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="https://wa.me/905330391565?text=Merhaba%2C%20proje%20hakk%C4%B1nda%20g%C3%B6r%C3%BC%C5%9Fmek%20istiyorum."
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-[#25D366] text-white px-10 py-4 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-[#1EBD5A] transition-colors"
          >
            WhatsApp'tan Yaz
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+905330391565"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-3 bg-gold text-charcoal px-10 py-4 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-[#B8965A] transition-colors"
          >
            0533 039 15 65
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </main>

